'''Mark Williams''' (born 27 March 1979) is an Australian-born American [[volleyball]] and [[beach volleyball]] player.<ref>{{cite sports-reference|Mark Williams|https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/wi/mark-williams-1.html|1 May 2014}}</ref>

Williams was born in [[Sydney]] but moved to the United States when he was nine years old. In 1999, while he was at [[UCLA Bruins|UCLA]], Williams trained with the [[Australia men's national volleyball team|Australian national indoor team]].<ref>{{cite web |title=Player Bio: Mark Williams |url=http://www.uclabruins.com/ViewArticle.dbml?SPSID=758510&SPID=128409&DB_OEM_ID=30500&ATCLID=208189251 |publisher=UCLA Bruins |accessdate=1 May 2014}}</ref> At the [[2000 Summer Olympics]] in Sydney, was a [[Volleyball#Libero|libero]] of the squad which placed eighth among 12 participating teams.<ref>{{cite web |title=Australia Volleyball at the 2000 Sydney Summer Games |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/countries/AUS/summer/2000/VOL/ |publisher=Sports Reference LCC |accessdate=1 May 2014}}</ref>

In 1998 he made his debut in beach volleyball with [[Larry Witt]] where they competed in [[Hermosa Beach]]. After graduating in 2001, he played in five [[Association of Volleyball Professionals|AVP]] events that year with several partners.<ref name="WilliamsBVBinfo">{{cite web |title=Mark Williams – Bio Bits |url=http://www.bvbinfo.com/player.asp?ID=1155 |publisher=Beach Volleyball Database |accessdate=1 May 2014}}</ref>

At the [[2004 Summer Olympics]] in [[Athens]], Williams qualified for the beach volleyball tournament alongside [[Julien Prosser]] after competing in the [[FIVB Beach Volleyball World Tour|FIVB Tour]] during the 2003 season.<ref name="WilliamsBVBinfo" /> They finished in fourth place after losing the bronze medal match to fifth-seeded team [[Patrick Heuscher]] and [[Stefan Kobel]] from Switzerland.<ref>{{cite web |title=Prosser, Williams miss beach volleyball bronze |url=http://www.abc.net.au/news/2004-08-26/prosser-williams-miss-beach-volleyball-bronze/2033134 |publisher=[[ABC Online]] |accessdate=1 May 2014}}</ref>

